tool_description: This API generates email which is valid for 10 minutes
title: Temporary Mail API

api_list.name: Temporary Mail generator
api_list.description: This end point takes a 'GET' request and returns generated mail.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://temporary-mail-api.p.rapidapi.com/generate_email"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "temporary-mail-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
